headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid TECH and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: While the S&P 500 is up 26.5% since April 2025, Bio-Techne (currently trading at $59.58 per share) has lagged behind, posting a return of 19.2%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
